g.text: Follow the technical constraints and concerns of the project
Use the defined project repository and setup a tool for project management
Add the necessary scripts to the project
Elaborate a Domain Model using DDD
Support and apply authentication and authorization for all its users and functionalities.
Process the files produced by the Applications Email Bot, so that they can be imported into the system by initiative of the Operator
Register, disable/enable, and list users of the backoffice
Register a customer and that the system automatically creates a user for that customer
Register a candidate and create a corresponding user
Register an application of a candidate for a job opening and import all files received
List all applications for a job opening
Display all the personal data of a candidate
Display all the personal data of a candidate, including his/her applications
Setup the phases of the process for a job opening
Deploy and configure a plugin (i.e., Job Requirement Specification or Interview Model) to be used by the system
Select the requirements specification to be used for a job opening
Select the interview model to use for the interviews of a job opening (for their evaluation/grading)
Generate and export a template text file to help collect the candidate answers during the interviews
Generate and export a template text file to help collect data fields for candidates of a job opening (so the data is used to verify the requirements of the job opening)
